INSTALLATION NOTES


1) Set the environment variable NUMERICSPATH, for example in csh

> setenv NUMERICSPATH /path/where/Numerics/is/located/

2) Choose the right Makefile.inc according to the target platform, for example

> cp Makefile.inc.linux Makefile.inc

3) Build library

> make lib

4)  build and run test

> make buildtest ; make runtest


